tourBios.exmtStatus: Conditional - Finished T114 at 2015 Web.com Tour Qualifying Tournament
tourBios.carHigh: 2012: Played in 12 events on the Gateway Tour, made six cuts and posted four top 10s.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Won the 2006 West Seattle Amateur...Recorded runner-up finish at the 2006 PNGA Men's Public Links Championship in Corvallis, Oregon...Won the 2005 Callaway Junior Series event at McCormick Woods Golf Course in Port Orchard, Wash.
tourBios.personal: First Tee intro song would be "Love Psalm" by Tribal Seeds...Has worked in landscaping and painted houses pursuing professional golf aspirations...Likes to play guitar and drums and would be in a band if not playing for a living...Would love the opportunity to play Augusta National, Bethpage Black and Merion GC...Only uses quarters that have the birth year of his brother or sister on them...Has met Andy Roddick at Plantation GC and Ray Allen while playing Aldarra GC...Best concert attend was Coachella...Would like to trade places with Nicolas Tesla while he was inventing technologies that were ahead of their time in hopes of understanding his brilliance...List attending a Formula-1 Race outside the United States at the top of his bucket list.
